先？</blockquote><br />\n好似英文定廣東話問我，之後講明呢條係英文 / 中文 / 普通話答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"966739819eaad3844a11f8503964ff250243a36c","tid":333485,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T04:42:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>港人搵食好難避開普通話，見工面試如果唔識較輸蝕</blockquote><br />\n見多幾份政府工先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前見民航處衰係普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n何國民航處？</blockquote><br />\n香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n乜唔係用英文咩？見工條友國語勁唔勁先？</blockquote><br />\n好似英文定廣東話問我，之後講明呢條係英文 / 中文 / 普通話答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實普通話易過英文好多。英文不濟人士先會用普通話打飛機，ff平起平坐。"},{"pid":"0532983232bb533d80f821e55319ea858f2bfb62","tid":333485,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:39:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜呢到無人知bbc中文咩人揸fit</blockquote><br />\n留意好耐"},{"pid":"32b9d0234543ab9e1d88ba909949bce896841b05","tid":333485,"uid":51532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:39:27.000Z","msg":"老實如果大陸唔比香港人講廣東話點算？"},{"pid":"2998a8fc03ded16b202ff94a34e150c5e3ba8ec5","tid":333485,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:44:52.000Z","msg":"咁又點？"},{"pid":"80af9496229bebfbe2c6ef82eff4ae4674e9c2cd","tid":333485,"uid":79979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:56:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>港人搵食好難避開普通話，見工面試如果唔識較輸蝕</blockquote><br />\n見多幾份政府工先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前見民航處衰係普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"